      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e317-102"><xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> または <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> で <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> アクションを使用して、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>を対話的に停止します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e317-102">Use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> action with an <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> or <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> to interactively stop a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e317-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> は、アクティブな場合にのみ <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> に影響します (<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> が開始した後)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e317-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> only affects a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> when it is active (after the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> starts).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e317-104">ストーリーボードを停止すると、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> イベントと <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> イベントはトリガーされますが、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> イベントはトリガーされません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e317-104">Stopping a storyboard triggers the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> events, but not the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e317-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> は <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> を直接参照しません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e317-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> does not reference a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> directly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e317-106">代わりに、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> は <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>を制御する <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> の <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> を参照する必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e317-106">Rather, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> must reference the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> that controls the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e317-107">例については、「[方法: イベントトリガーを使用してストーリーボードを制御する](/dotnet/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts)」を参照してください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e317-107">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](/dotnet/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts) for an example.</span></span>  
  
## <a name="pause-resume-stop-or-otherwise-control-a-storyboard-interactively"></a><span data-ttu-id="2e317-108">ストーリーボードを対話的に一時停止、再開、停止、または制御する</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e317-108">Pause, Resume, Stop, or Otherwise Control a Storyboard Interactively</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="2e317-109"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> を対話的に一時停止、再開、または制御できるようにするには、その <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> の <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> プロパティを設定し、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> オブジェクト (<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>など) を使用して、その <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>を参照して制御します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e317-109">To be able to pause, resume, or otherwise control a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> interactively, set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> property of its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> and use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> object (such as <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>, or <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>) to control it by referencing its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e317-110"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> の <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> が指定されていない場合、開始後に <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> を対話的に制御することはできません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e317-110">If the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> is unspecified, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> cannot be interactively controlled after it is begun.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2e317-111">詳細については、「[方法: イベントトリガーを使用してストーリーボードを制御する](/dotnet/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts)」を参照してください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e317-111">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](/dotnet/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts) for more information.</span></span>  
  
